                <p>Görsel estetik, kullanıcı arayüzü ve genel sanat yönetimi.</p>
                <span class="special-prize-reward">(Ödül Yakında Açıklanacak)</span>
              </div>
              <div class="special-prize-card">
                <h4>🧩 Temaya En Uygun Oyun Ödülü</h4>
                <p>Verilen temayı en yaratıcı ve derinlikli şekilde işleyen projeye.</p>
                <span class="special-prize-reward">(Ödül Yakında Açıklanacak)</span>
              </div>
              <div class="special-prize-card">
                <h4>🎮 En İyi Oynanış Ödülü</h4>
                <p>Mekanik bütünlük, eğlence faktörü ve akıcı kontrol hissi.</p>
                <span class="special-prize-reward">(Ödül Yakında Açıklanacak)</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- ═══ CRYPTOGRAPHIC THEME TEASER ═══════════════════════════════ -->
      <section class="theme-teaser-section" id="tema">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="theme-teaser-card fade-in" id="theme-teaser">

            <!-- Header -->
            <div class="theme-teaser-header">
              <div class="theme-teaser-header-left">
                <span class="lock-icon">🔒</span>
                <span class="theme-teaser-header-title">Etkinlik Teması</span>
              </div>
              <span class="classification">Sınıflandırılmış</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Body -->
            <div class="theme-teaser-body">
              <p class="theme-teaser-label">Tema Açılış Tarihine Kadar Kilitli</p>

              <!-- Digital Countdown Timer -->
              <div class="theme-countdown-container" id="theme-countdown">
                <div class="theme-countdown-item">
                  <span class="theme-countdown-value" id="t-days">00</span>
                  <span class="theme-countdown-label">GÜN</span>
                </div>
                <span class="theme-countdown-separator">:</span>
                <div class="theme-countdown-item">
                  <span class="theme-countdown-value" id="t-hours">00</span>
                  <span class="theme-countdown-label">SAAT</span>
                </div>
                <span class="theme-countdown-separator">:</span>
                <div class="theme-countdown-item">
                  <span class="theme-countdown-value" id="t-mins">00</span>
                  <span class="theme-countdown-label">DAKİKA</span>
                </div>
                <span class="theme-countdown-separator">:</span>
                <div class="theme-countdown-item">
                  <span class="theme-countdown-value" id="t-secs">00</span>
                  <span class="theme-countdown-label">SANİYE</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <style>
                .theme-countdown-container {
                  display: flex;
                  justify-content: center;
                  align-items: center;
                  gap: 1.5rem;
                  font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
                  color: var(--cyan-accent);
                  margin: 2.5rem 0;
                  text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.4);
                }
                .theme-countdown-item {
                  display: flex;
                  flex-direction: column;
                  align-items: center;
                  min-width: 80px;
                }
                .theme-countdown-value {
                  font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
                  font-weight: 700;
                  line-height: 1;
                  letter-spacing: 2px;
                }
                .theme-countdown-label {
                  font-size: 0.7rem;
                  color: var(--text-muted);
                  margin-top: 0.8rem;
                  letter-spacing: 3px;
                  font-weight: 600;
                }
                .theme-countdown-separator {
                  font-size: 2.5rem;
                  margin-top: -1.5rem;
                  opacity: 0.4;
                  color: var(--text-muted);
                }
                @media (max-width: 768px) {
                  .theme-countdown-container { gap: 0.8rem; margin: 1.5rem 0; }
                  .theme-countdown-item { min-width: 60px; }
                  .theme-countdown-value { font-size: 1.8rem; }
                  .theme-countdown-separator { font-size: 1.2rem; margin-top: -0.8rem; }
                  .theme-countdown-label { font-size: 0.6rem; letter-spacing: 1px; }
                }
              </style>

              <script>
                function initThemeCountdown() {
                  const target = new Date('2026-05-15T10:00:00+03:00').getTime();
                  const daysEl = document.getElementById('t-days');
                  const hoursEl = document.getElementById('t-hours');
                  const minutesEl = document.getElementById('t-mins');
                  const secondsEl = document.getElementById('t-secs');

                  if (!daysEl) return;

                  function update() {
                    const now = new Date().getTime();
                    const diff = target - now;

                    if (diff <= 0) {
                      if (daysEl) daysEl.textContent = '00';
                      if (hoursEl) hoursEl.textContent = '00';
                      if (minutesEl) minutesEl.textContent = '00';
                      if (secondsEl) secondsEl.textContent = '00';
                      clearInterval(timer);
                      return;
                    }

                    const d = Math.floor(diff / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24));
                    const h = Math.floor((diff % (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24)) / (1000 * 60 * 60));
                    const m = Math.floor((diff % (1000 * 60 * 60)) / (1000 * 60));
                    const s = Math.floor((diff % (1000 * 60)) / 1000);

                    if (daysEl) daysEl.textContent = String(d).padStart(2, '0');
                    if (hoursEl) hoursEl.textContent = String(h).padStart(2, '0');
                    if (minutesEl) minutesEl.textContent = String(m).padStart(2, '0');
                    if (secondsEl) secondsEl.textContent = String(s).padStart(2, '0');
                  }

                  const timer = setInterval(update, 1000);
                  update();
                }
                document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', initThemeCountdown);
              </script>

              <!-- Fake decryption progress bar -->
              <div class="theme-progress-bar">
                <div class="theme-progress-track">
                  <div class="theme-progress-fill" id="theme-progress"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="theme-progress-label">
                  <span>Şifre Çözülüyor...</span>
                  <span id="theme-progress-pct">0%</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <p class="theme-teaser-hint">
                Tema <strong>15 Mayıs, 10:00</strong>'da açılış töreninde duyurulacaktır.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Footer -->
            <div class="theme-teaser-footer">
              <span class="neon-pulse"></span>
              Dosya bütünlüğü doğrulandı — SHA-256: e3b0c44298fc1c14...
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

